<% govspeak_for :body do %>


  <% if calculator.adjusted_ssl_loan_amount > 0 %>
    <%= render partial: 'disclaimer_lle' %>

    As you are over 60, you are not eligible for a Tuition Fee Loan or a Maintenance Loan. You could get a Special Support Loan of <%= format_money(calculator.adjusted_ssl_loan_amount, pounds_only: true) %>. This is a loan to help with living costs.
  <% else %>
    Your result is an estimate. You’ll be told your exact amount, including any extra student funding, after your application is approved.

    You are not eligible for a Tuition Fee Loan, Maintenance Loan or Special Support Loan.
  <% end %>

  <%= render partial: 'extra_student_funding_lle', locals: { calculator: calculator } %>

  <%= render partial: 'next_steps_lle' %>
<% end %>
